Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:04.52,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:10.20,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I want to be by your side more than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:15.29,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go take a walk in chains of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:54.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Enemy at the {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Snowy Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:54.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Enemy at the {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Snowy Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:40.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:40.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Silver Advent Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for calling you all the way to Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to ask this of you upon your arrival, Miss Vallière,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I would like you to wield your magic for the sake of your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we are, the Lowscythe Military Port,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is our final destination, Albion's capital, Londinium.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, the enemy's line of defence is located\Nbetween these two places, at the city of South Gotha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We predict a large resistance against our invasion into this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I would like you to eradicate the soldiers in the city of South Gotha with your Void magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like you did against the force that marched into Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the battle were to break out within the city, civilians would get dragged into the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do my best to meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came all the way to Albion because Her Highness summoned us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but, in the end, we're being used for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said this many times. I don't want to kill nor be killed, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, "I will do my best to meet your expectations" my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do is fly this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can't if you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness is seeking help from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From {\i1}me{\i0}, someone who's been ridiculed for\Nbeing unable to use magic since her childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly tell her I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're nearing the place we were told to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you able to control your Void magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rol'n Suny, Feely, Jalunsa, Kusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Os, Sumy, Rodde,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyn, Rade, Beozzs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, she released all of the energy she had charged throughout her life during the critical moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't magic that can be used freely to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around! I'll do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around now. That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've spotted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean I'm in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, they took out the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has yet to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There do not appear to be changes in the enemy lines either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tactic of utilising Void seems to have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:05:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to have depended on unreliable magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only remaining choice is to charge into them head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the order to march into the city of South Gotha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Louise and Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hesitated in shooting the enemy, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what happened because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemies are human, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei's letter told me to not get used to killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I apologise to Her Highness for this failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our tactic failed because you couldn't use your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, you stupid dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck, you're so disgusting. Stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't stick together, we'll freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You're not a child, so blow your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could die at any moment for having to make a shelter in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'd be better if we both strip and use our body heat to warm each other up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You perverted dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I bet Partner had a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was killed by none other than the girl he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying strange things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you loved me and all, but I never gave you a reply,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can't die on me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! That was a good sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, you don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This aristocratic girl was naked all night{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magistrate Sheffield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemy has sent its forces to the city of South Gotha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to send reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the troops stationed there to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And while doing so, have them take as much of the city's food supply as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food supply?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they occupy the city, being unable to\Nreplenish their food supply would be a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to stop them there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, what will happen to the citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An iron dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have crash-landed in the\Nmountains around the city of South Gotha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the one that appeared when we marched into Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find this iron dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The retreat is in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind the pilot dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he unconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like his leg's been wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, carry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll freeze to death at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, you bit my head off for hesitating to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to forsake a wounded person,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my reputation as an aristocrat would be tarnished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... aristocrat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect my honour even at the cost of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what aristocrats do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me Del!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or because you'd tarnish your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... wouldn't call this a wound... if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an aristocrat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the war nor killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I only care about protecting Louise and making it home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we argue here, we'll both die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you must fight, do so after we get off the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked it up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be saying words of gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't have to be so spiteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiteful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by spiteful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you trying to warn your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you become so almighty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog! You dog! You dog! You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.59,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! Stop it, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to go to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering... how I should report our failure to Her Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply tell her exactly what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I failed."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm troubled over it because that won't cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness... gave me this mission because she had faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't meet her expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what else can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you commit seppuku as atonement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seppuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means cutting open your stomach. Your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I come from, that's what they used to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was only joking around. Don't take it seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's more presentable than simply returning home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Her Highness is at war with thousands of soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your one success or failure won't make much difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like you say, my duty might not be anything meaningful,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm an aristocrat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a full-fledged mage, I have to be of use to Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't do that, then it's better to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the aristocrats from Tristain were wusses,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:14:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never imagined a girl like you\Nwould have such an admirable attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're young, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably about the same age as us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise de La Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the legendary sword, Delflinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least tell us your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henry Stanford of the Albion Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's not a dragon, but a new magic weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a military secret, so I can't tell you any more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why it was faster than Winzar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winzar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, it died in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was your treasured partner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was an important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was alive until this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the only reason I didn't freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why apologise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't kill, you get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the midst of war, I don't want to become a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whether or not it's for the sake of the country, I do not wish to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor do I want to kill others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who rode right into the middle of the enemy's base on the new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you fight for, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's to protect the person I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can fight if that's the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting the person you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not only for Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, everyone at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Princess of Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's in danger, I would want to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I would refuse to kill anyone for the sake of politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it bother you, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not an aristocrat, so he doesn't\Nunderstand the concept of pride and honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in dying or killing others for those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honour is the most important thing for an aristocrat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fighting for your loved ones", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd... like to say that one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice to live solely for the sake of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aristocrats wouldn't hesitate to break up with the one they love if it's for the sake of honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person in your picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you... say goodbye to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? Person in the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I applied to the military after dissolving the engagement with my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to live through this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if the war continues, I'll eventually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't return alive, I have no choice but to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst man alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that you're the worst man ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare mock an aristocrat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you're an aristocrat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying for the sake of honour is something an idiot does!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take insults from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Do you want to die that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henry, you're a {\i1}human{\i0} before being an aristocrat, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living through it no matter what and returning to her side... doesn't that thought cross your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting cool by saying "die" all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When an aristocrat goes off to war, he must prepare for death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's strange to have a death wish from the outset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death... comes at the very end, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until that time comes, do your best at living!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's exactly it, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henry, live and make it back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and marry her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the engagement was dissolved, I'm sure she's still waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for you to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rabbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was gunfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, they must be here to capture you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot. I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon knight of the Albion Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up in a fight with the enemy and dropped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they fell on the other side of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other side, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paying back debts is what aristocrats do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the enemy's dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the sparkle and get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, let us all live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Julio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes asked me to search for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, my mission is to help Her Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you two are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't be of any help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has abandoned the city of South Gotha, and we were able to seize it without any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing for you to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I must atone for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you're not thinking{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give me any mission regardless of its danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To fight and to die for Your Highness is the greatest honour for us aristocrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You encouraged him to live, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is honour that important to you, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a cat for you, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Silver Advent Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
